rComments: funny guy, extremely easy grader. can honestly say i learned very little and skated by with an A.

Great teacher, enthusiastic and has a ton of stories to relate to the subject. Not too hard of a class and overall amazing. Wears great hats to class too. overall goofball and likes to just take fun tangents but still gets the information through.

Very friendly, his class itself was as interesting as history gets.  He tends to talk too much about Roman coins, so mush so that it became funny.  Also, at 90 minutes long non-history majors may not be able to sit for the entire session, but the easiness of the class makes it worth while.
Excellent teacher. Very funny. Made the class much more interesting. Tests are easy (He leaves it up to the class to decide the format).
